<includeonly><span style="font-variant:small-caps">{{{1}}}</span></includeonly><noinclude>

Usage:
<pre>
{{small-caps|text}}
</pre>

This template renders text in small caps. Example:
<pre>
{{small-caps|Large and Small}}
</pre>
gives: {{small-caps|Large and Small}}.

You can use <code><nowiki>{{sc|text}}</nowiki></code> as an abbreviation.

[[Category:Templates]]

</noinclude>